A simple Class for Feed Forward Neural Networks built on top of Numpy. 

Back propagation is fully vectorized matrix form.
If you are curious about the derivation of these equations see the here:

https://rojasinate.com/#myWork

Notes:
There is an experimental feature (rswitch). It pretty much acts like drop out but currently
I haven't worked out the kinks. 

